Title: A Place Beneath the Boughs
Description:
Thanks to you and all the mortals who defended the Emerald Dream, a new World Tree now grows in the Dragon Isles.

Amirdrassil's boughs will be a haven of peace and tranquility, and a place of respite for the kaldorei souls lost at Teldrassil.

Tyrande Whisperwind and Shandris Feathermoon are at the tree now. They would share words with you.
ObjectivesText: Meet Tyrande and Shandris in Amirdrassil.
